== jQuery UI Live Chat (juichat) ==

* Using jQuery and jQuery UI for themeing
* Written in PHP using MySQL
* Designed to be like: <a href="http://anantgarg.com/2009/05/13/gmail-facebook-style-jquery-chat/">Gmail/Facebook Style jQuery Chat</a> (but 100% free!)
* <a href="http://os.alfajango.com/css-emoticons/">jQuery CSS3 Emoticons</a>
* Licensed under LGPL

== Demo ==
* http://juichat.com/

==Options:==
* heartbeat: delay in time to check for new chats/viewers
* idle_user: delay in time before a user is idle (yellow)
* display_viewers: show the viewers
* viewer_wrapper: the class name or div for viewer list
* emoticons: enable emoticons
* page: the php page
